OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright start, cloud
OL,6,Fthickening quickly this morning with
OL,7,Frain developing, turning heavy and
OL,8,Fpersistent as it moves into Argyll
OL,9,Fwith hill snow there. A drier spell in
OL,10,Fsouth before heavy rain returns along
OL,11,Fwith strengthening winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FFurther heavy rain this
OL,14,Fevening turning showery but winds
OL,15,Fincreasing to gale or severe gale for
OL,16,Fa time. Winds easing overnight with
OL,17,Fskies clearing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
