OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA dry bright start. Clouding
OL,6,Fover for a time with some showers,
OL,7,Fsnow on hills, then brighter again
OL,8,Flater.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,11,Fwith some sunny spells on Monday then
OL,12,Fhigh cloud later. Sunny, breezy and
OL,13,Fwarm on Tuesday, cloudier later.
OL,14,FChance of patchy or rain or showers on
OL,15,FWednesday.
